{
  "stem": "1061.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because I mean, if we had lice-- I mean a woman like this, this SS woman, she probably would spit on me if she ever-- or kill me if she ever saw lice on me, you see.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they gave us under the barracks-- where the kitchen was and all that-- they gave us a place to live.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were bunks there, but we did not-- we were not allowed to sleep in the regular barracks.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because after all, you know, if you come to clean her office and then something would you bring some sicknesses from the others, I mean, you know.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So this was Retzow.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And this is now February, 1945.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And some people were already liberated, those who stayed behind in Poland.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And for us, there was no end.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I couldn't even imagine how liberation would come.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I, I couldn't even-- to put it in the most far-fetched [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] picture.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You know, the bombs started falling, so we knew that something was now happening, which we're hoping will really be the end, that whether they kill us with the bombs is better than everything.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Because I mean, we might yet be sent again and sent again.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And who knows where we will finally end up, right?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But the point is that-- you-- you asked me before if I had a plan.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I not only had no plan, I had not even the imagination to conjure up a picture of how will it all come about.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, you're a child and you read books, and there are-- you know, when people get liberated, there are parades, and the band is playing, and the flags are flying, and people are throwing flowers.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It didn't fit the picture.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
